  "text": "To study the SDBI+FI model, we can consider the double scaling limit γ → 0 with γθ = −8 √ 2π 2 ξ fixed, as explained in (3.14) . In this limit, the value ofκ in (3.48) gives the value in (2.47). Hence the result (3.49) also agrees with the explicit computation (2.51) in the last section based on the non-linear formalism. Therefore, this also provides a non-trivial test of the non-linear supersymmetric formalism of [CITATION_1] .",
